## Write a program to find sum of n natural numbers

```
Input  : 5
Output : 15
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="find-sum-of-n-natural-numbers" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main(){

    int n,sum=0;;
    scanf("%d",&n);
    for(int i=1;i<=n;i++) sum+=i;
    printf("%d",sum);
    return 0;
}

//Contributed by Raghav Garg
```

